# Context: E-commerce Serverless (Py3.11, Terraform, Clean Arch)

# LAMBDA IMPORTS (Runtime: /var/task/)
- Internal: Sibling imports only (from service import...)
- Shared: From layers (from shared.db import...)
- Local: Prioritize Lambda syntax.

# STANDARDS
- Flow: Handler -> Service (Logic) -> Repository (SQL).
- Pydantic V2 (schemas.py) | SQL: Parameterized only.
- Tools: aws_lambda_powertools | Pytest (Mocks only).
- Comments: None, unless business logic is high complexity.